<title>USA: Mercantile says to buy Illinois bank.</title>
<headline>Mercantile says to buy Illinois bank.</headline>
<dateline>ST. LOUIS 1996-08-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>Mercantile Bancorp said it will acquire Regional Bancshares Inc for $41 million in cash and stock.</p>
<p>Regional is a one-bank holding company that operates the Bank of Alton, a $175 million-asset bank located in Madison County, Illinois, Mercantile said.</p>
<p>Regional shareholders will get 23.7 Mercantile shares plus $485.76 for each Regional share, Mercantile said.</p>
<p>Mercantile also said it completed its acquisition of Peoples State Bank, of Topeka, Kansas.</p>
<p>--Chicago Newsdesk 312-408-8787</p>
